\par }{\b\f1\fs22 
\par 3. Read the passage given below and identify one quality that it describes to become an authorized teacher of Bhagavad gita.
\par }\pard \ri270\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright {\f1\fs18 
\par }\pard \li270\ri270\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright {\f1\fs22 One has to receive the instructions of the Supreme Lord through the disciplic chain of spiritual masters. As described in Bhagavad-gita Fourth Chapter Text 2:
\par }\pard \nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright {\f1\fs22 
\par }\pard \qc\li270\ri270\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright {\i\f1\fs22 evam parampara-praptam imam rajarsayo viduh 
\par }\pard \qc\li270\ri270\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright {\i\f1\fs22 sa kaleneha mahata yogo nastah parantapa
\par }\pard \qc\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright {\i\f1\fs22 
\par }\pard \li270\ri270\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright {\b\f1\fs22 This supreme science was thus received through the chain of disciplic succession, and the saintly kings understood it in that way. But in course of time the succession was broken, and therefore the science as it is appears to be lost.
\par }{\f1\fs22 
\par The guru does not manufacture a new process to instruct the disciple. The guru gives the disciple the same transcendental knowledge which he received from his spiritual master. This is called the system of disciplic succession. This is the bona fide Vedic system of receiving the spiritual knowledge from a bonafide guru by which the Supreme Personality of Godhead is pleased. The bona fide spiritual master is he who has received the knowledge from his guru, who in turn is bona fide because he has received the knowledge from his guru. This is called the }{\i\f1\fs22 parampara }{\f1\fs22 system.
\par }\pard \nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright {\f1\fs18 
\par Please write your conclusion in the box below :
\par }{\fs18\lang1024 {\shp{\*\shpinst\shpleft144\shptop164\shpright9361\shpbottom1029\shpfhdr0\shpbxcolumn\shpbypara\shpwr3\shpwrk0\shpfblwtxt0\shpz2\shplid2052{\sp{\sn shapeType}{\sv 1}}{\sp{\sn fFlipH}{\sv 0}}{\sp{\sn fFlipV}{\sv 0}}{\sp{\sn fillBackColor}{\sv 16711680}}{\sp{\sn fFilled}{\sv 1}}{\sp{\sn lineWidth}{\sv 3175}}{\sp{\sn fShadow}{\sv 0}}}{\shprslt{\*\do\dobxcolumn\dobypara\dodhgt8194\dprect\dpx144\dpy164\dpxsize9217\dpysize865\dpfillfgcr0\dpfillfgcg0\dpfillfgcb255\dpfillbgcr255\dpfillbgcg255\dpfillbgcb255\dpfillpat1\dplinew5\dplinecor0\dplinecog0\dplinecob0}}}}{\f1\fs22 
