\par 
\par }{\b\f1\fs22 
\par 4. Read the passage given below and identify one quality that it describes to become an authorized teacher of Bhagavad gita.
\par }{\f1\fs22 
\par                             }{\i\f1\fs22 idam tu te guhyatamam pravaksyamy anasuyave
\par                             jnanam vijnana-sahitam yaj jnatva moksyase 'subhat
\par }{\b\f1\fs22 \ldblquote My dear Arjuna, because you are never envious of Me, I shall impart to you this most confidential knowledge and realization, knowing which you will be relieved of the miseries of material existence.\rdblquote 
\par }{\f1\fs22 So, the first qualification is }{\i\f1\fs22 anasuyave}{\f1\fs22 . }{\i\f1\fs22 Anasuyave}{\f1\fs22  means one who is not envious. A person generally... all conditioned souls, they are envious of God, envious. "Why He should be God? I am God. I am God." So Arjuna is not like that person. Therefore he is speaking to Arjuna. He is devotee. In the Fourth Chapter also, He said }{\i\f1\fs22 bhakto 'si priyo 'si.}{\f1\fs22  Therefore Krishna does not expose Himself unless one is free from envy to Him. This is first qualification. The so-called }{\i\f1\fs22 jnani}{\f1\fs22 , yogis, they cannot understand. It is not possible, because they are trying to become God. Although it is simply dream, no one can become God, but they are envious, that "Why Krishna should be God? I can also become god." }{\i\f1\fs22 Anasuyave}{\f1\fs22 . Krishna said to Arjuna that "I am speaking to you knowledge, }{\i\f1\fs22 jnanam, sa-vijnanam}{\f1\fs22 , with scientific understanding." }{\i\f1\fs22 Jnanam te'ham sa-vijnanam pravaksyami anasuyave}{\f1\fs22 . "Because you are not envious. That is your qualification. You are very submissive student free from envy. Therefore I'll give you most confidential knowledge."}{\b\f1\fs18 
\par 
\par }{\f1\fs18 Please write your conclusion in the box below :}{\b\f1\fs18 
\par }{\fs18\lang1024 {\shp{\*\shpinst\shpleft144\shptop202\shpright9361\shpbottom1067\shpfhdr0\shpbxcolumn\shpbypara\shpwr3\shpwrk0\shpfblwtxt0\shpz3\shplid2053{\sp{\sn shapeType}{\sv 1}}{\sp{\sn fFlipH}{\sv 0}}{\sp{\sn fFlipV}{\sv 0}}{\sp{\sn fillBackColor}{\sv 16711680}}{\sp{\sn fFilled}{\sv 1}}{\sp{\sn lineWidth}{\sv 3175}}{\sp{\sn fShadow}{\sv 0}}}{\shprslt{\*\do\dobxcolumn\dobypara\dodhgt8195\dprect\dpx144\dpy202\dpxsize9217\dpysize865\dpfillfgcr0\dpfillfgcg0\dpfillfgcb255\dpfillbgcr255\dpfillbgcg255\dpfillbgcb255\dpfillpat1\dplinew5\dplinecor0\dplinecog0\dplinecob0}}}}{\b\f1\fs18 
